Supplement on Payment Services
:SKRSLUT.
.sp 5mm
:SWISS8.
This supplement is a translation of the document "Tillæg om
betalingstjenester til de almindelige forretningsbetingelser
- erhvervskunder" and is for information only. The Danish version of the
document is the legally binding document and applies to any commitment
entered into between you and vestjyskBANK.
.sp 5mm
:SWISS10.
:FED.
Introduction
:SKRSLUT.
:SWISS8.
.sp 3mm
This supplement describes your rights and obligations when using
vestjyskBANK's payment services, such as:
.sp 3mm
.of 3mm
*¤depositing of cash into a payment account,
.sp 3mm
.of
.of 3mm
*¤withdrawal of cash from a payment account,
.sp 3mm
.of
.of 3mm
*¤execution of a payment transaction to a payment account, in-
.br
cluding credit or card transactions,
.sp 3mm
.of
*¤transfer of money.
.sp 3mm
.kp off
.kp on
This supplement focuses on the concepts of payment transaction, payment
account, business day and value date.
.sp 3mm
.kp off
.kp on
:KURSIV.
Payment transaction
:SKRSLUT.
.br
Transactions initiated by a payer or a payee with a view to paying,
transferring or withdrawing funds irrespective of any underlying
obligations between the payer and payee.
.sp 3mm
.kp off
.kp on
:KURSIV.
Payment account
:SKRSLUT.
.br
A payment account is an account established for the purpose of completing
payment transactions. Your trading account, for instance, is covered by
this definition.
.sp 3mm
.kp off
.kp on
:KURSIV.
Business day
:SKRSLUT.
.br
A business day is a day on which the payer's or payee's provider, charged
with the completion of a payment transaction, is open for business as
required in order to complete the transaction.
.sp 3mm
.kp off
.kp on
:KURSIV.
Value date
:SKRSLUT.
.br
The value date is the day on which a deposit, withdrawal or other account
movement affects the calculation of interest.
.sp 5mm
.kp off
.kp on
:SWISS10
:FED.
Rules specific to payment services
:SKRSLUT.
:SWISS8.
.sp 3mm
In addition to this supplement on payment services, vestjyskBANK's special
terms and conditions on payment services apply, such as vestjyskBANK's
Dankort terms or online banking agreements.
.sp 5mm
.kp off
.kp on
:SWISS10
:FED.
Execution of payment transactions
:SKRSLUT.
:SWISS8.
.sp 3mm
For vestjyskBANK to execute transactions on your behalf, you must
provide the reg. no. and account no. of the account from which funds are to
be withdrawn.
.sp 3mm
.kp off
.kp on
In the case of domestic transfers, you must provide the reg. no. and
account no. of the account into which funds are to be transferred.
.sp 3mm
.kp off
.kp on
In the case of international payment transactions, you must provide IBAN
and SWIFT code.
.sp 3mm
.kp off
.kp on
On payment of joint inpayment forms, you must provide the relevant creditor
number.
.sp 3mm
.kp off
.kp on
A payment order is deemed to have been correctly executed when executed
using the unique identification code stated in the payment order.
.sp 3mm
.kp off
.kp on
A precondition for vestjyskBANK executing your payment orders is that
sufficient funds are available in the relevant account.
.sp 5mm
.kp off
.kp on
:SWISS10
:FED.
Payment order
:SKRSLUT.
:SWISS8.
.sp 3mm
A payment order pay be placed:
.sp 3mm
.of 3mm
*¤by contacting vestjyskBANK in person
.sp 3mm
.of
.of 3mm
*¤via your online banking facility
.sp 3mm
.of
.of 3mm
*¤by forwarding a letter to vestjyskBANK.
.sp 3mm
.of
.kp off
.kp on
A payment order is deemed to be received on the business day on which
vestjyskBANK receives the payment order.
.sp 3mm
.kp off
.kp on
A payment order received at the end of a business day is deemed to be
received on the next business day on which it will be executed. For further
information on the deadline for receipt of payment orders to be executed on
the same day, please contact vestjyskBANK.
.sp 5mm
.kp off
.kp on
:SWISS10
:FED.
Withdrawal, rejection and reversal of payment
.br
order
:SKRSLUT.
:SWISS8.
.sp 3mm
Once vestjyskBANK has received your payment order, it cannot be withdrawn.
.sp 3mm
.kp off
.kp on
Payment orders registered for execution at a later date, however, may be
withdrawn on or before the end of the previous business day at the latest.
.sp 3mm
.kp off
.kp on
You can withdraw a payment order via your online banking facility or by
contacting vestjyskBANK. vestjyskBANK reserves the right
to charge a withdrawal fee.
.sp 3mm
.kp off
.kp on
If your payment order is rejected due to factual errors, vestjyskBANK will
notify you of the reason for the rejection and of the procedure initiated
to correct the error causing the rejection. vestjyskBANK reserves the
right to charge a fee for this service.
.sp 3mm
.kp off
.kp on
vestjyskBANK reserves the right to charge a fee for attempting to reverse
funds if the unique identification code stated by you is incorrect.
.sp 5mm
.kp off
.kp on
:SWISS10
:FED.
Maximum execution time
:SKRSLUT.
:SWISS8.
.sp 3mm
The amount of a payment order will always be withdrawn from your account on
the date of payment agreed to by you and vestjyskBANK. Up to three business
days may elapse from the date on which the amount is withdrawn from your
payment account until the amount is deposited into an account with the
payee's bank.
.sp 3mm
.kp off
.kp on
In the case of hardcopy payment orders, execution time may be up to four
business days. This applies, for instance, to inpayment forms or forms that
you complete in vestjyskBANK in connection with international payment
transfers.
.sp 3mm
.kp off
.kp on
The same applies if you ask your bank by letter or e-mail to make a money
transfer on your behalf.
.sp 3mm
.kp off
.kp on
Where an amount is transferred to your payment account, vestjyskBANK may
deduct any fees and charges incurred in connection with the transfer before
depositing the amount in your account.
.sp 3mm
.kp off
.kp on
:SWISS10
:FED.
Information on payment transactions
:SKRSLUT.
:SWISS8.
.sp 3mm
If, in the course of one month, payments have been made to and from your
payment account, information relating to these payments is available via
your online banking facility on a daily basis. vestjyskBANK may charge
a fee for this service.
