:SWISS10
:FED.
Checking payment transactions
:SKRSLUT.
:SWISS8.
.sp 3mm
You are obliged to check any entries on your account. If you detect
transactions that do not correspond to your receipts or that you have not
made, please contact vestjyskBANK as soon as possible.
.sp 5mm
.kp off
.kp on
:SWISS10
:FED.
Unauthorised payment transactions
:SKRSLUT.
:SWISS8.
.sp 3mm
If you find that one or more transactions on your payment account have not
been authorised or made by you, please contact
vestjyskBANK as soon as possible
after noticing the unauthorised transaction. When assessing whether or not
you have contacted vestjyskBANK in due time, importance
will be attached to your
duty to check your account on a regular basis. In any case, you must
contact vestjyskBANK not later than two months after the execution of the
transaction.
.sp 5mm
.kp off
.kp on
:SWISS10
:FED.
Interest calculation and availability
:SKRSLUT.
:SWISS8.
.sp 3mm
.us Interest calculation on deposits into your payment account
.br
On a cash payment into your payment account, the value date is the business
day following receipt of the funds.
.sp 3mm
.kp off
.kp on
.us Interest calculation on withdrawals from your payment account
.br
Where an amount is withdrawn from your payment account, the value date is
the business day on which the amount is withdrawn from your account.
.sp 3mm
.kp off
.kp on
.us Availability of the transferred amount
.br
An amount deposited into your payment account is at your disposal right
away. The amount, however, is not at your disposal if deposited on a day
which is not a business day in vestjyskBANK.
.sp 3mm
.kp off
.kp on
.us Availability of cash deposits
.br
A cash deposit into your payment account will be at your disposal
immediately upon receipt.
.sp 5mm
.kp off
.kp on
